Load Data to Staging Area 10

1.      Use Data Flow Task to cleanse data as in screenshot below:


2.      Use SELECT in conjunction with InitCap() function (created in the prepare data warehouse environment stage) and CAST Statements in T-SQL with the OEL DB source/connection manager to [dbo].[CraigsListSTG] to conform the data types using SQL Command below:

 

SELECT  CAST(id AS BIGINT) AS ID,

               dbo.InitCap(region) Region,

               CAST(price AS MONEY) AS Price,

               CAST([year] AS INT) AS Year,

               dbo.InitCap(manufacturer) Manufacturer,

               dbo.InitCap(model) Model,

               dbo.InitCap(condition) Condition,

               CAST(LEFT(LTRIM(cylinder), CHARINDEX(' ', LTRIM(Cylinder))) AS INT) AS 'Cylinders',

               dbo.InitCap(fuel) Fuel,

               CAST(odometer AS INT) AS Odometer,

               dbo.InitCap(titleStatus) TitleStatus,

               dbo.InitCap(transmission) Transmission,

               vin VIN,

               UPPER(drive) Drive,

               dbo.InitCap(size) Size,

               dbo.InitCap(vehicleType) 'Vehicle Type',

               dbo.InitCap(paintColor) 'Paint Color',

               UPPER(LEFT(LTRIM(state),2)) AS 'State',

               CAST(lat AS FLOAT) AS 'Latitude',

               CAST(Long AS FLOAT) AS 'Longitude'

FROM    [dbo].[CraigsListSTG]


3.      Use Derived Column transformation to replace NULL values for the indicated columns with default values as below screenshot and table for clarity: 


 

#

Derived Column Name

Expression

1

uStrRegion

TRIM(Condition) == "" || ISNULL(Condition) ? "NotProvided" : LEFT(Condition,50)

2

uStrManufacturer

TRIM(Fuel) == "" || ISNULL(Fuel) ? "NotProvided" : LEFT(Fuel,50)

3

uStrModel

TRIM(Model) == "" || ISNULL(Model) ? "NotProvided" : LEFT(Model,50)

4

uStrCondition

TRIM(Condition) == "" || ISNULL(Condition) ? "NotProvided" : LEFT(Condition,50)

5

uStrFuel

TRIM(Fuel) == "" || ISNULL(Fuel) ? "NotProvided" : LEFT(Fuel,50)

6

uStrTitleStatus

TRIM(TitleStatus) == "" || ISNULL(TitleStatus) ? "NotProvided" : LEFT(TitleStatus,50)

7

uStrTransmission

TRIM(Transmission) == "" || ISNULL(Transmission) ? "NotProvided" : LEFT(Transmission,50)

8

uStrDrive

TRIM(Drive) == "" || ISNULL(Drive) ? "NotProvided" : LEFT(Drive,50)

9

uStrSize

TRIM(Size) == "" || ISNULL(Size) ? "NotProvided" : LEFT(Size,50)

10

uStrVehicleType

TRIM([Vehicle Type]) == "" || ISNULL([Vehicle Type]) ? "NotProvided" : LEFT([Vehicle Type],50)

11

uStrPaintColor

TRIM([Paint Color]) == "" || ISNULL([Paint Color]) ? "NotProvided" : LEFT([Paint Color],50)

12

uStrState

TRIM(State) == "" || ISNULL(State) ? "ZZZZZ" : LEFT(State,5)

13

VIN

TRIM(VIN) == "" || ISNULL(VIN) ? "NotProvided" : VIN

 

Note that the columns will mainly be Unicode data type and will need to be converted to non-Unicode type in the stage following.
